title: Official results of Egyptian parliamntry polls' 1st stage to be announced Thursday - Egypt Elections 2015 - Egypt
text:
The results of the first stage of Egypt's parliamentary elections will be announced on Thursday, the High Elections Committee (HEC) announced in a press conference late Monday.
The vote count process has already started, shortly after the end of voting.
